snippet.textDisplay:
Ummm..as much I am a huga Kpop fan! Nd more importantly,an Allu fan! Man ,i dont think kpop nd indian music combining is great idea. Considering where v r now,there r ppl still close minded abt the idea of kpop. Im afraid it wuld invite more haters. Smthg which we've already have in abundance of,nd it wuld be sad if ppl frm India also r part of it. 

Fusion of Traditional tempos of both these worlds might be interesting nd culd work. Coz both of them have similarities more or less. 
Also ,lowkey i dont want the indian teenagers to get influenced by these kpoppers in a bad way like dieting to look slim like them,dreaming to become a kpop star like em without knowing the hardships,atrocities along wid it.
